                  </hi>. I am clerk to James Pridmore Bryan—the <hi rend="italic">Sophia</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Mary</hi> do not belong to him, but the coals that were in them do. <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> There was a barge at the top of another; I saw a man screening coals—I went and picked them up for him.</p>
